## 🟢 Low Priority / Already Handled

| Item | Status |
|------|--------|
| Background patterns (GridPattern, BlueprintPattern, etc.) | ✅ Pure CSS backgrounds — no JS cost |
| Marquee animations (AchievementsMarquee, SkillTicker) | ✅ CSS `animation` with `will-change: transform` and `translate3d` — GPU-composited |
| Lenis mobile skip | ✅ Already disabled on mobile (line 15-19) |
| `backdrop-blur` GPU hint | ✅ Already has `transform: translateZ(0)` + `will-change` in globals.css |
| `unoptimized` hero image | ⚠️ Minor — serves full-res PNG. Consider optimized Next.js Image. |

