| 1 | SkillIcon float → CSS animation | 15 min | 🔥🔥🔥 Eliminates ~27 JS loops |
| 2 | Lenis + GSAP → single RAF loop | 5 min | 🔥🔥🔥 Eliminates dual RAF |
| 3 | Hero mousemove → RAF throttle | 5 min | 🔥🔥 Stops layout thrashing |
| 4 | ContactSection clock → isolated component | 5 min | 🔥🔥 Stops 1/s full re-render |
| 5 | PlatformCard mousemove → RAF throttle | 5 min | 🔥🔥 3 cards × 60fps savings |
| 6 | Navbar scroll → passive + RAF | 5 min | 🔥 Scroll perf |
| 7 | Preloader interval → RAF | 5 min | 🔥 Startup perf |
| 8 | ProjectSlider blur → contain + will-change | 3 min | 🔥 Composite perf |
| 9 | FeatureCardRow maps → useMemo | 2 min | ⚡ Minor |
| 10 | ActivityHeatmap → single IntersectionObserver | 10 min | ⚡ Section perf |
